metadata.description:
Meet Carpe DIEm: the world's seven greatest, colour-coded assassins (one
for each day of the week, though everybody hates Mondays).

When danger calls, they're sent to whack the planet's deadliest and most
outrageous villains -- from demon-summoning chefs to hordes of killer clowns!
metadata.name: A1: Carpe DIEm
